{"title":"枣林村集〔三首〕","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣林村集〔三首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老书记回村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋山妩媚秋水娇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳似火烧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京开罢群英会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老书记回村了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未等走进乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里的小伙子迎上了道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个接兜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个接包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们不住把手招。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未等走进村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾草的孩子便围上了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个叫背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个让抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更小的攀在腿上打吊吊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走呵走呵已听见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远近近小鸡子叫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走呵走呵已望见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系天线的枣树梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不得一步跨进村呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老书记急着问候大家好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心急又不住把脚停呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因又记挂庄稼的旱和涝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过大渠撬棵草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰见牲口捋捋毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东望望，西瞧瞧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西红柿早拉了秧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萝卜白菜早种好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棒子大，豆荚饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！一月不见全熟了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走呵走呵，走进村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻惯的饭香满街飘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过饲养室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见那马驹子已上套；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过会计室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又听见十二位的算盘打得正热闹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干得好呵干得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员心劲大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部兴致高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后问磅秤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定超产破指标……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老书记想着想着嗤嗤笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下惊哑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边草丛的蛐蛐叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚进队室门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰见贫协主任大老赵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——咳！当是谁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原是书记回来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该早捎个信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"套车接一遭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——接个啥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下边没长两只脚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老书记回来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老书记回来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人上前争着问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席可好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城可好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——都好！都好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带回一片毛主席的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他也问候大家好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还带回主席著作一大包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留待秋后办夜校；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还带回来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还带回来了——大寨的山呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一渡河的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山巍巍呵水滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习这革命精神向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一楼更比一楼高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王老汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天还没亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗还发暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼哒哒风响摇门扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十岁雇农王老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茧手捧着一张纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸页轻轻颤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是想了一夜等不及，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多来添麻烦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼下就秋收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家试新镰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀磨到缸沿上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀刃晃人眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可年轻人太毛糙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢穗子掉粒没人管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从地里，到场院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该空洒多少血和汗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十头上当长工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十出头花了眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当长工，花了眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却看清了千般苦和难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那日子，为一粒谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩膀头挨过三扁担；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那日子，为一把米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麻绳子吊了个月牙弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日大丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能忘从前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社长讲——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗粒要入库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得人人做保管；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天找你写封信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给社里的货郎担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让他给捎副老花镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好上第一线！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天还没亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗还发暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大清早我象已看见："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他正蹲在那地边边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一穗穗拾呀一粒粒拣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手心捧着的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪是粮和米？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的好江山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收　肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东一座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西一座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房檐一样高呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子一样宽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马棚的腥臊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊栏的膻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑油油的优质肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆堆都是宝贝蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走来了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打方收肥的评议组；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带头的——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是贫协组长张老汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盘皮尺一把锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腋窝下还挟个红算盘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨家走呀挨家收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨家丈量挨家算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻一锨，瞧一眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咳，一堆更比一堆好，还用看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算盘珠子打了个全堂满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆盘皮尺也嫌短。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少个早，多少个晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶着雾拾呀踏着露拣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙换炕，忙起圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一箕子一铲都是汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不象过去——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好肥都送自留地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今爱队的心呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗都象块红火炭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打方的小组刚走过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉肥的大车甩炸了鞭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹄声中一声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今天拉走千车肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天定拉回粮万石！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}